            </li>
            <li>delay or failure in receiving data</li>
            <li>indirect damages arising from you using the service or relying on its content</li>
            <li>
                the content and availability of external websites that link to the service or which are linked from it
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="app-button-group__wrap">
    <div class="app-button-group">
        <button class="app-button" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("TermsAccept", "Terms")'">Accept</button>
        <button class="app-button app-button--secondary"
            onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("TermsDecline", "Terms")'">Decline</button>
    </div>
</div>
